  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/3ab4c4490a4ce8e3ddf8113dd861aeb2.avif?t=1762175590\" width=396 height=127 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/94a6b128470eb3dc745d6cc5f88d01ea.avif?t=1762175590\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a world shaped by Charlie's anger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore wonderful places and meet zany characters. Help them solve their comical problems by solving funny puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll need to carefully examine your surroundings and talk to the inhabitants of Asfalia to prevent the volcano from erupting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dialogues are full of humor and irony, with cultural references that make the adventure just as enjoyable for adults. That's right, Asfalia is for everyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/3a7f91247a6e37deb4f57e2e1e98b65c.poster.avif?t=1762175590\" width=780 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/3a7f91247a6e37deb4f57e2e1e98b65c.webm?t=1762175590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/3a7f91247a6e37deb4f57e2e1e98b65c.mp4?t=1762175590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/56d0c0b6cd0c6f3a719731095702bc44.avif?t=1762175590\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Asfalia</i> is aimed at children aged 7 and up, as well as adults curious to discover an adventure rich in humor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The puzzles are fun and easy to solve, and the controls are intuitive, making the game easy to pick up and play. Asfalia can be played entirely with a mouse or a controller, making it perfectly compatible with the Steam Deck. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's ideal for long journeys with children, for example: a game that can be played anywhere, with ease!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/5adcdd0fc7c9215438961d4fa21d5c66.avif?t=1762175590\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a big tantrum, Charlie wakes up in a mysterious world threatened by a gigantic volcano about to erupt. Warning: this world is as beautiful as it is unpredictable...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Asfalia is a hand-painted world with a unique and enchanting style. It is a wonderful universe populated by adorable and mischievous characters inspired by Alice in Wonderland, Inside Out, and The Little Prince.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/39298d7392731562e9d5763b68bfa5e9.avif?t=1762175590\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hermit dwarf, rebellious student cups, an adventurous fork, a DJ salmon... The world of Asfalia is overflowing with characters that are as zany as they are endearing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Professional dubbing in French and English, lively voices, and a carefully crafted soundscape immerse you in a vibrant adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/cde00cad3282c8de6772f018d4c627c3.poster.avif?t=1762175590\" width=780 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/cde00cad3282c8de6772f018d4c627c3.webm?t=1762175590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/cde00cad3282c8de6772f018d4c627c3.mp4?t=1762175590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/a803e5e9f0b862f9971825a658e37688.avif?t=1762175590\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of Asfalia is full of fun puzzles and crazy riddles that are easy to solve!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you manage to build the musical bridge? Will you find out what's scratching the giant cactus? Or will you save the salmon lava-party?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/7df08588f06c051fa15fb2b5cceff363.avif?t=1762175590\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with the environment and you can add to your sticker collection. But be careful, some are well hidden... ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/18300d906c3482c53aed2d58cc722c37.poster.avif?t=1762175590\" width=780 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/18300d906c3482c53aed2d58cc722c37.webm?t=1762175590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/18300d906c3482c53aed2d58cc722c37.mp4?t=1762175590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/2c6b1ee28c72240336a707710c83bd32.avif?t=1762175590\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In short, Asfalia is a world full of endearing and funny characters, with a captivating narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Asfalia: The Cranky Volcano</i> is just the first chapter of this journey. A vibrant world is calling you... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's go to Asfalia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675040/extras/bd955f198157caad033b61e84aeb7f3e.avif?t=1762175590\" width=396 height=127 /></span></p>",
